'''Glazion energy torches''' were powerful cutting tools. The walls of the bunker used by the [[Five Families of Cestus Cybernetics|Five Families]] of [[Cestus Cybernetics]] were reputed to be so thick that it would take one standard day for a glazion torch to penetrate them.

